content.rendered:
Directed by Sashi Kiran Tikka.

Written by Abburi Ravi. Rahul Pakala. Sashi Kiran Tikka. Adivi Sesh.

Cast Adivi Sesh(Gopi / Arjun Kumar). Sobhita Dhulipala(Sameera Rao). Jagapathi Babu(Raghuveer / Rana). Prakash Raj(Satya). Irfan Ahmed Syed(Ravi varma (as Irfan)) . Ademi(Arabic Trainer). Neelsh Ahankari(Customs Officer). Ali(Saudi Guy #3). Ashok(Rajahmundry Constable #2). Adarsh Babu(Chittagong Terrorist #2). Harshad Babu(Chittagong DVD Shop Boy). Harika Devi Balla(Air Hostess). Tammareddy Bharadwaja((as Bharadwaja Thammareddy)). Ramana Bhargava(Gokaraju). Rohit Chachu(Guy In Pub). Sakshi Chaturvedi(Girl In Pub). Chetan(Trinetra Photographer). Mohan Chowdary(Nursery Raju). Veerendra Chowdary(Politician).Mozammel Hoshen Chowdhury. Darshan(Young Gopi). Deepak(Salesman At Tailorman). Sanjay David Dorakala(Airport Police). Mahendar Harijam(Auto Driver #2). Prem Jeevan(TV9 Reporter Rajahmundry). Pradeep Katukuti(Indian Agent in Climax). Khalid Khan(Rajahmundry Constable #1). Nayeem Khan(Immigration Officer). Vennela Kishore(Shaam). Kanij Koirala(Hamzaa). Jyothi Prasad Kondapalli(Arjun Friend #2). Kiran Kumar(Librarian). Madan Kumar(Arjun Friend #3). Anish Kuruvilla(Damodar). Anu Kushwaha(Immigration Lady). Mir Madani(Airport Traveller). Abhiram Mannem(Saudi Guy #2). Faraz Maroof(Weapon Handling Trainer). 

Language Telugu.

Producers Abhishek Agarwal. Sujith Kumar Kolli. Vivek Kuchibhotla. Abhishek Nama. T.G. Vishwa Prasad. Vijaya Rajesh. Krish Siddipalli. Krishna Siddipalli. Kittu Suryan.

Production Abhishek Pictures. People Media Factors. Vista Dream Merchants.
